response.overview: Erik, Ryan, and Cooze start college and pledge the Beta House fraternity, presided over by none other than legendary Dwight Stifler. But chaos ensues when a fraternity of geeks threatens to stop the debauchery and the Betas have to make a stand for their right to party.
response.tagline: The most outrageous slice of pie!
response.title: American Pie Presents: Beta House

titles.title: American Pie presenta La casa Beta
